==English==

===Adjective===
'''invidious'''
# [[envious|Envious]]; causing or arising from [[envy]].
# [[enviable|Enviable]]; [[desirable]].
# Prompted by or expressing or adapted to excite envious [[dislike]] or [[ill will]]; offensively or unfairly [[discriminate|discriminating]]: as, invidious distinctions or comparisons.
# [[hateful|Hateful]]; [[odious]]; [[detestable]].

